Let $P$ be a point inside triangle $ABC$.  Let $G_1$, $G_2$, and $G_3$ be the centroids of triangles $PBC$, $PCA$, and $PAB$, respectively.  If the area of triangle $ABC$ is 18, then find the area of triangle $G_1 G_2 G_3$.

[asy]
import geometry;

